comments: Williams (BOS) establishes himself in a legal position in Bridges' (PHX) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the pick.
Ayton (PHX) moves alongside of Tatum's (BOS) path to the basket and absorbs the body contact created by Tatum.
Walker (BOS) and Booker (PHX) arrive at the loose ball simultaneously and the body contact that occurs is marginal.
Bridges (PHX) makes contact to Walker's (BOS) head that affects his driving shot attempt. Replay review of the shooting foul called on Bridges pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Williams (BOS) briefly places two hands on Ayton's (PHX) body off ball but he immediately removes both hands. The contact is marginal.
Pritchard (BOS) and Bridges (PHX) briefly engage in marginal contact off ball prior to disengaging.
Williams (BOS) establishes himself in a legal position in Booker's (PHX) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the pick.
Walker (BOS) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) dislodges Johnson (PHX) from his legally obtained position during the rebound.
Pritchard (BOS) reaches in and makes contact to Paul's (PHX) arm that affects his ability to move freely.
